# lychee URL-exclusion patterns (regex, per DECISIONS.md D-4).
# Keep these tight: only intentional placeholders and known-flaky citations.
# Real internal broken links are fixed at the source, not hidden here.

# Intentional template/example placeholders, not real links.
# Sources: commands/stack-recommend.md output format (<URL>),
# docs/adr/template.md (NNNN-...), evals/scenarios/template.md (XXXX-...).
/URL$
/NNNN-
/XXXX

# Flaky external citation kept in the docs (real URL; lychee reports an
# HTTP/2 protocol error against this host). Excluded so a network quirk does
# not fail the build; the citation stays in wos/insurance-compliance.md.
fcc\.gov/document/fcc-closes-tcpa
